#

Avocado Corn Salad

10 min
$8.5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

SaladFreshHealthyEasy

Description

A refreshing and vibrant salad combining creamy avocado with sweet corn, perfect for a light meal or side dish.

Ingredients

  • avocado: 2, diced
  • fresh corn: 1 cup, cooked and cooled
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • red onion: 1/4 cup, finely chopped
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
